"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069320/extras/17b26bd7882423cb868df9f984980e60.poster.avif?t=1771332566\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069320/extras/17b26bd7882423cb868df9f984980e60.webm?t=1771332566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069320/extras/17b26bd7882423cb868df9f984980e60.mp4?t=1771332566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIGHT YOUR WAY OUT</h2>Clear your way through three different floors of the tower, filled with dangers and hazards around every corner. Each floor tells a different piece of the story of the tower for you to uncover.<br><br>Will you be able to escape?",
